data.description: Perfect location in North Murfreesboro in established Primm Springs with triple Siegel Schools When you pull into the driveway you're greeted with a three-car garage. This 5-bedroom home will take your breathe as you enter the foyer. Enjoy entertaining your guest while cooking in the chef style Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and hard surface counter tops. On the main level, you'll find a beautifully appointed Master bedroom and en suite featuring and tiled shower area. Laundry facilities are also available for your convenience. Upstairs boasts natural light with 4 additional guest bedrooms.
